content.question: On the template provided, draw bars in the appropriate locations to predict the relative probability of success for the nest in the presence of predators where: • the cuckoos were added to the nest containing only warblers (group 1) • the cuckoos were removed from the nest containing warblers and cuckoos (group 2)
